{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC03_LIN_510.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1d,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Linca, why don't we have lunch now?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I have been waiting for those words.<CR>I was reaching my hunger limit."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x38,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Hehehe, it's nothing fancy, but I made lunch for us. Here you go."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Ooh, then if I may... *munch*"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Th-This is...delicious!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x39,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Whew... Good. I was worried it might not suit your taste."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "So alchemy can even be used to make these kinds of things..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "N-No, that's not it.<CR>I made them normally."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x165,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Normally? Then Ayesha, you can cook?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha, well, I'm not good enough to go around telling everyone I can cook..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x167,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "No, this is admirable. It is not something that is easily done."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "I-I wouldn't take it to that extent..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "...Ayesha, I have a special favor to ask of you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "I know it is improper for a bodyguard like me to ask for favors, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "I was hoping you could listen to my pleas."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "What's wrong? You're so proper...<CR>I'll listen, as long as you're okay<CR>with someone like me..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x11,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Actually, I have been given a mission to master the techniques of processing ingredients."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "However, even though I have cut wild beasts, I have never cut vegetables."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "It is quite easy to slice a beast that is more than twice my height, but I find ingredients to be most difficult to cut."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "It seems like normally the opposite is true..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, will you please instruct me on the secrets of cooking?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Well, I'm not sure about the secrets of cooking, but it's nice for girls to know how to cook..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Okay. If you're okay with having me for a teacher, I'll do it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Wait, but wouldn't Marion be able to teach you?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x165,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "She told me to use my head first."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x167,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "However, I do not know where to even start when it comes to cooking..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "I-I see. I understand your situation. Then, umm, would it be okay if I can get ready first?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Of course! That would be very helpful!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "(I'm not to a point where I can teach anyone... I need to study up, myself.)"
        }
    ]
}